    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 996-generation Carrera 4S features the iconic wide-body silhouette and a robust M96 3.6L flat-six engine delivering linear power through a precise 6-speed manual transaxle. The all-wheel-drive system provides exceptional mechanical grip, complemented by a factory-tuned suspension and four-piston monoblock calipers for superior deceleration. Recent service includes the critical IMS bearing retrofit and a new rear main seal, ensuring the valvetrain and bottom end remain reliable. The chassis is taut, exhibiting minimal bushing deflection, and the throttle response remains sharp. A driver-focused example that perfectly balances analog engagement with daily usability.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
