    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and reliability. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish, though close inspection reveals minor road-pebble chips on the front bumper and a small superficial scratch near the rear wheel well\u2014typical for a car of this vintage that has been enjoyed. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of comfort; the premium leather upholstery is supple with no tears, and the wood grain accents remain vibrant. All electronic components, including the panoramic sunroof, dual-zone climate control, and the premium audio system, function flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is sound. It has a comprehensive service history with synthetic oil changes performed every 5,000 miles. Most recently, the brake pads were replaced and the tires were rotated. The engine runs quietly, and the transmission shifts smoothly through all gears. This is a solid, dependable vehicle ready for its next owner to drive home with confidence.",
